lead_paragraph: Derrick Favors had 16 points, 10 rebounds and six blocked shots to power the Utah Jazz over the Denver Nuggets 85-81 Wednesday night, extending their season-best winning streak to four games.

headline.print_headline: Derrick Favors Powers Jazz to 85-81 Win Over Nuggets
